title: Control
description: A portrait of Ian Curtis, the enigmatic singer of Joy Division whose troubled life ultimately led him to suicide. Based on the memoirs of Deborah Curtis. (2007)

title: Snow Cake
description: The heart-warming story of an unlikely friendship between and autistic woman, and a man left traumatised after a car accident. (2005)

title: Jack Irish: Dead Point
description: When a high profile judge commissions Jack Irish to locate a mysterious red book, Jack is thrown into a world of sexy club owners, drug dealers and unhinged killers. (Movie 3 of 3) (2013)
